        "ts-node": "^10.9.2",
        "typescript": "^5.7.3"
    },
    "description": "**ChainPay Africa** is a decentralized bill payment platform that allows users to pay for services like electricity, internet, and more using cryptocurrency wallets instead of traditional banks. Built on the **CrossFi Chain**, it enables fast, low-cost, and borderless transactions.",
